hopobject.body: I can't stand football duratia india A Department of Health Spokesperson said: “There are many fantastic examples of really good food across the NHS thanks to forward thinking and innovative staff. But, we recognise that there is too much variation across the country – that is why we have implemented a tough new inspection programme. With our army of thousands of patient assessors we will drive up standards and reduce variation in hospital food.
